        "subject": "LU-8191 utils: non-static functions in lustre_rsync.c",
        "message": "LU-8191 utils: non-static functions in lustre_rsync.c\n\nStatic analysis shows that a number of functions\ncould be made static. This patch declares several\nfunctions in lustre_rsync.c static.\n\nMaking lr_get_FID_PATH() static surfaced new\nformat-truncation errors. Check the return code of\nsnprinf() to silence these.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: I4f437357b01261f8b5690339cda3ae47c1ab1f67\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
